    • Constructor Detail

      • ConfluenceClient

        public ConfluenceClient​(java.lang.String baseUrl,
                        java.lang.String user,
                        java.lang.String password,
                        boolean server)
        Authentification is enabled with basic auth. Check "curl -v http://url-to-atlassian?os_authType=basic If basic auth enabled, the "WWW-Authenticate: Basic realm="protected-area" is returned
        Parameters:
        baseUrl - Url to the server, could be http or https
        user - Plain-Text of user to log in
        password - Plain text of password
        server - true if dedicated server, false if cloud server
